{"tid":303961,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"還返《今晚打喪屍》原著畀我！屌那星果個毒撚導演＋四方雞","createTime":"2017-06-30T14:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T16:20:19.000Z","uid":5379,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd2f5caef4a5c9db98dc7c0d88dfcbd14ee0857","tid":303961,"uid":5379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:08:46.000Z","msg":"屌那星隻方形雞做乜撚嘢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身係余兒fans，睇晒原著1、2集連漫畫都睇埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身本書好撚好笑又有熱血位，背後仲有d隱喻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見電影宣傳做得咁好咁勁，首MV又正，諗住一心支持本地電影入場啦，抱住好高期望<br />\n<br />\n點知越睇越火，d演員其實ok<br />\n但你老味原來成套戲根本同原著無關，亂撚咁改，連個世界觀都改哂，d人物變晒，對白小學雞，最後結局唔知佢噏乜春 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻仆街方形雞，黐撚線㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完完全全侮辱原著同原作者。原著好睇好多<br />\n真心戥余兒好慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黐撚線喺邊度出嚟㗎個導演 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c103fc128dc3b82c47d856082f1422968175d54","tid":303961,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:23:47.000Z","msg":"有張繼聰同白只合作本身好大期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入場就係為左等睇頭半part佢哋兩個互放笑料，間唔中j下顏卓靈黃敏奕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後半part就好爽咁用新奇武器打打打喪屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母點知全套野9唔答8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 9up多過做，全套戲唔係9up就係9跑，再慢慢睇住個角色變喪屍前多謝曬所有祖宗至捨得死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇左20分鐘已經想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 臨尾播卡通片真心屌左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇到我全場黑人問號樣，到底我睇左d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌"},{"pid":"b8b5cdfe2fdda342bb893a9a4fa680fdca8d98d6","tid":303961,"uid":42848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"想聽導演講法，個ending好似比人剪過咁,<br />\n出左credit仲有片唔係以為咁都有得偷雞拍續集呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d505766def860b4bb43e46e8476a621babaf7aa","tid":303961,"uid":40461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:57:19.000Z","msg":"睇左，真係好垃圾，編劇同導演應該禁止以後唔可以再拍片"},{"pid":"ec3711beb6671841e72b41d1586572b851182654","tid":303961,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇左，真係好垃圾，編劇同導演應該禁止以後唔可以再拍片</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc16bf0f3954379a10d4b5e647b6c6d6d31fb486","tid":303961,"uid":269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌那星隻方形雞做乜撚嘢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身係余兒fans，睇晒原著1、2集連漫畫都睇埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身本書好撚好笑又有熱血位，背後仲有d隱喻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見電影宣傳做得咁好咁勁，首MV又正，諗住一心支持本地電影入場啦，抱住好高期望<br />\n<br />\n點知越睇越火，d演員其實ok<br />\n但你老味原來成套戲根本同原著無關，亂撚咁改，連個世界觀都改哂，d人物變晒，對白小學雞，最後結局唔知佢噏乜春 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隻仆街方形雞，黐撚線㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n完完全全侮辱原著同原作者。原著好睇好多<br />\n真心戥余兒好慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黐撚線喺邊度出嚟㗎個導演 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=